sets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n之後去埋7樓個殘廁到扑埋（7樓冇班房 所以好靜）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n往事只能回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc601ae3bb43c65b6ee4158916a4be53f848844","tid":414544,"uid":16864,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"同條大波妹同學座最後個行<br />\n成日互抽水上上下堂伸手入去摸西 無咩毛<br />\n佢又得閒無事 摸我條撚<br />\nchock到扯其<br />\n有次拎我條撚出來 含左幾啖"},{"pid":"56d511923685b0433ee3ed9efe4e9a426633268e","tid":414544,"uid":51393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T11:58:37.000Z","msg":"經過見到say hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16d1c6b616986a2121e992435faa2e9302f188f","tid":414544,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"行樓梯仆街食波餅<br />\n<br />\n唔好相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d852376952da00b838bfb1134ea215364f8c3f","tid":414544,"uid":113277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"真事：<br />\n<br />\n中七阿哥去左外國讀書，屋企人去旅行時，就叫班fd 上屋企玩，當中有女仔特別淫，平時我地講咸野佢都唔會歧視我哋，仲笑笑口加把嘴。<br />\n<br />\n個晚又上我度，飲酒玩到醉醉地，二男一女攬住瞓(我無份，毒能一條)。事後二男話有渣到波&amp;摷到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eb2b0dca317981dbfddc3c3cdf5be1114ebe6e","tid":414544,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"視姦佢"},{"pid":"fb02e38ec8019cd7256465281091173bf6b2cabb","tid":414544,"uid":135344,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:31:49.000Z","msg":"果陣中三<br />\n調位坐係個大波女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常樣 但大波加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢織頸巾有支長長地唔尖既棒<br />\n上堂果陣成日用支捧插入去佢件衫格甩底個位<br />\n係咁duk佢個波 好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又唔出聲 又用d調皮聲叫我咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2387b6ed564f8c8ca493911a6295f244cd5a6e29","tid":414544,"uid":92459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"係街係我側面攬埋黎，可惜係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一個，坐我隔籬位既女同學聽唔清楚我講咩，然後成個身哄埋我心口到，隻耳靠到好近我個嘴，聞到少少香味，真係好正，咁多年黎都未有野可以令我呆咗，但係我果一刻真係呆咗係到，完全俾唔到反應，中學生涯少有令我回味既畫面。<br />\n<br />\n雖然第一個有身體接觸，但係第二個感覺正十倍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad307750e04ade1d3284dfbe835705a69fbab3f4","tid":414544,"uid":88479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"女班長記我名"},{"pid":"4851429bc087d520763fbbabd01ce88fb2198c5b","tid":414544,"uid":40940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全部上堂既<br />\n<br />\n我就中學果陣一班人係m記吹水食野打機<br />\n佢就係我隔離果陣狂渣我jer 我<span style=\"color: red;\">隔著褲卒佢下面</span> 之後佢偷偷同我講:你搞到我好想要<br />\n<br />\n細個唔識 之後無做特別野<br />\n<br />\n佢大個女又拍緊拖<br />\n間唔中而家我地一班人都食飯<br />\n我見到佢就每次都諗咸野</blockquote><br />\n😕"},{"pid":"8d583204b8bf5daba69c56b968e6f7212a227a0a","tid":414544,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"同佢傾計"}]}